OL,6,FCornish residents and visitors are
OL,7,Fbeing reminded that they should only
OL,8,Fcall 999 or visit the Royal Cornwall
OL,9,FHospital's emergency department if
OL,10,Ftheir "illness or injury is life-
OL,11,Fthreatening". This includes chest
OL,12,Fpain, trouble breathing, severe
OL,13,Fbleeding, stroke and loss of
OL,14,Fconsciousness.
